NEG PF-AF-roundabout CORE.SG wind
`The wind did not blow around'

# a simple sentential negation with aux 'di' without any abs/erg cases
Source: author
Vetted: f
Judgment: g
Phenomena: {negation}
Di  naglaylay ti      sabong
di  n-ag-laylay ti      sabong
Neg PF-AF-wilt   CORE.SG flower.ABS
`The flower didn't wilt'

# sentential negation with aux 'di' with any abs enclitic
Source: author
Vetted: f
Judgment: g
Phenomena: {negation}
Diak        nagsangit
di=ak       n-ag-sangit
Neg=1SG.ABS PF-AF-cry
`I did not cry'

# ungammatical: sentential negation 'di' is not for negating NP-only
Source: author
